  - who: Sirius
    text: NY THE GODDESS WHAT ARE YOU???
    voice: {fileID: 0}
    answers: []
  - who: Splingo
    text: Hello friend!! My name is Splingo! What is your name?
    voice: {fileID: 0}
    answers: []
  - who: Sirius
    text: You stand before Sir Lady Sirius, THE UNRELENTING! State your purpose FIEND!!
    voice: {fileID: 0}
    answers: []
  - who: Splingo
    text: Thank you for asking friend!! :D i'm here to greet new arrivals to our
      amazing carnival!
    voice: {fileID: 0}
    answers: []
  - who: Splingo
    text: Yip Yip! Let me show you around, friend!!!
    voice: {fileID: 0}
    answers: []
  - who: Sirius
    text: You wish to challenge Sir Lady Sirius the unrelenting!?
    voice: {fileID: 0}
    answers: []
  - who: Sirius
    text: Prepare to feel my unrelenting fury, knave!!
